#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.235"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.235:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.235:0.2"
msgid "24. Āvāsikavagga"
msgstr "24. A Resident Mendicant"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: anukampakasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an5.235:0.3"
msgid "235. Anukampasutta"
msgstr "235. A Compassionate Mendicant"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.264"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: gihīnaṃ → gihiṃ (s1-3) | gihī (katthaci)
msgctxt "an5.235:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato āvāsiko bhikkhu gihīnaṃ anukampati."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, a resident mendicant with five qualities shows compassion to "
"the lay people."

msgctxt "an5.235:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi?"
msgstr "What five?"

#. VAR: Adhisīle → adhisīlesu (s1-3)
msgctxt "an5.235:1.3"
msgid "Adhisīle samādapeti;"
msgstr "They encourage them in higher ethics."

msgctxt "an5.235:1.4"
msgid "dhammadassane niveseti;"
msgstr "They equip them to see the truth of the teachings."

msgctxt "an5.235:1.5"
msgid "gilānake upasaṅkamitvā satiṃ uppādeti:"
msgstr ""
"When they are sick, they go to them and prompt their mindfulness, saying:"

msgctxt "an5.235:1.6"
msgid "‘arahaggataṃ āyasmanto satiṃ upaṭṭhāpethā’ti;"
msgstr "‘Establish your mindfulness, good sirs, in what is worthy.’"

msgctxt "an5.235:1.7"
msgid ""
"mahā kho pana bhikkhusaṃgho abhikkanto nānāverajjakā bhikkhū gihīnaṃ "
"upasaṅkamitvā āroceti:"
msgstr ""
"When a large mendicant Saṅgha is arriving with mendicants from abroad, they "
"go to the lay people and announce:"

msgctxt "an5.235:1.8"
msgid ""
"‘mahā kho, āvuso, bhikkhusaṃgho abhikkanto nānāverajjakā bhikkhū, karotha "
"puññāni, samayo puññāni kātun’ti;"
msgstr ""
"‘A large mendicant Saṅgha is arriving with mendicants from abroad. Make "
"merit! Now is the time to make merit!’"

msgctxt "an5.235:1.9"
msgid ""
"yaṃ kho panassa bhojanaṃ denti lūkhaṃ vā paṇītaṃ vā taṃ attanā paribhuñjati, "
"saddhādeyyaṃ na vinipāteti."
msgstr ""
"And they eat whatever food they give them, coarse or fine, not wasting a "
"gift given in faith."

msgctxt "an5.235:1.10"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato āvāsiko bhikkhu gihīnaṃ "
"anukampatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"A resident mendicant with these five qualities shows compassion to the lay "
"people.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.235:1.11"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
